summary:
This enb is settled in Visuals and Graphics because its based on my previous enbs.
It is dark and atmospheric. I used a style which had good feedback and boosted it up with newer and more subtle effects. On top of this, it has great performance even on mid-spec systems
descriptionHtml:
[center][i]The guy who brought you
Heartless Kinetao ENB
bitterSWEET ENB
and
Aliaris ENB[/i]


[size=5][i][b]Revink ENB[/b][/i][/size][/center]
Most enb presets are colorful and bright. They try to give a natural feeling. Some focus on photorealistic visuals, dark shadows, bright lights. And a few presets impress with unique bloom shaders, complex depth of field etc. .

But this does not try to line up with those. It is dark, greyish and unwelcoming like Skyrim itself.

This dark enb preset is based on the heartless kinetao and utilises redone shaders. 



okay, this enb uses the 132 binaries from enbdev.com
[url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0132.htm]here you go[/url]

open up the wrapper version and drop the d3d9.dll file into your skyrim main folder. 
My preset goes there as well. Copypaste the content of the "Revink ENB" folder.

And that´s it
author: LaBeatBeatbox
